trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart" />, <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart" />, and <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona compatibilidad en tiempo de diseño para los controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart" />, <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart" /> y <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner> is a multi-purpose designer that provides design-time rendering for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> controls, which both inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> base class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner> es un diseñador multiuso que proporciona el tiempo de diseño de representación para <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> y <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> controles, que heredan de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> clase base.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner> serves as a standard control designer, adding only what customization is needed to validate the associated control and apply its design mode state to the design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner> actúa como un diseñador de control estándar, agregando solo la personalización necesaria para validar el control asociado y aplicar su estado de modo de diseño a la representación en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: If you have a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> control, you can create a derived designer, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner>, to provide design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: Si tienes un personalizado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> (control), puede crear un diseñador derivado, como <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner>, para proporcionar la representación en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: You can safely override any of the members as needed; however, when overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A> method, be sure to call the base implementation to avoid losing design mode state information.
trans-unit.target: Se puede reemplazar de forma segura cualquiera de los miembros según sea necesario; Sin embargo, al reemplazar el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A> método, asegúrese de llamar a la implementación base para evitar la pérdida de información de estado de modo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner> share an identical interface and functionality.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner> y <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner> compartan una interfaz idéntica y la funcionalidad.

trans-unit.source: For an applicable code example, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner> class overview.
trans-unit.target: Para obtener un ejemplo de código aplicable, vea la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner> Introducción a la clase.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart" /> control to render at design time.
trans-unit.target: Crea una copia del control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart" /> asociado que se va a representar en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: A copy of the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart" /> control.
This method is overridden to copy zone information to the view control.
trans-unit.target: Este método se invalida para copiar información de zona en el control de vista.

trans-unit.source: Verifies that the control resides in a zone of type <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase" />, and then gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Comprueba que el control está en una zona de tipo <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase" /> y que obtiene el marcado que se utiliza para representar el control en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: The markup that is used to represent the control at design time, or error markup if the control does not reside in a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase" />.
trans-unit.target: El marcado utilizado para representar el control en tiempo de diseño o el marcado del error si el control no reside en <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart" />-derived control associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: Control derivado de <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart" /> asociado al diseñador.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart" />-derived control.
trans-unit.target: Enlaza el diseñador al control derivado de <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart" /> asociado.
